UPDATED - 8/17/18

FINAL PRICING - ACROSS THE BOARD 10% DISCOUNT ON LISTED PRICES, FREE SHIPPING ON ORDERS OVER $100.  ON THE ONE YEAR ANNIVERSARY OF MY FIRST LISTING (8/20/18), CARDS WILL NO LONGER BE AVAILABLE, SO IT'S NOW OR NEVER! THANK YOU TO EVERYONE WHO HAS SHOWN INTEREST.  CHEERS, TIM. 

***WILL ALSO CONSIDER TRADES WITH PSA GRADED SOUTHERN LEAGUE, T206 HOF CARDS, OR T212 SERIES***

I concede defeat.  The monster has won!  My monster number reached 429 and I have decided to move on to other challenges and sell off a big chunk of my PSA Graded T206 collection.  And I believe the Net54baseball folks deserve first dibs!

Here are the rules of engagement.  

(1), PRICES ARE FIRM,  please don't try to negotiate.  I believe my prices are very fair.  I will offer a 10% discount for every dollar spent over $250, and each order will have a fixed $5.00 shipping charge no matter how many cards are ordered.  By way of example, if an order is for $800.00, the 10% discount applies for every dollar over $250, so the discount would be 10% x $550 = $55 off.      
(2) First come, first serve.  The first person to communicate "I will take ..." via PM or e-mail at [url]jtlake67@att.net[/url] gets the card(s).  You are welcome to post a reply to the post, but I'm going to go by the time stamp of the message in cases where multiple parties express interest.
(3) Paypal F&F only.  If payment is not received within 48 hours of me acknowledging the order, I reserve the right to cancel the transaction.
(4) I cannot guarantee that the availability list will be updated every day.  So please don't get frustrated if I tell you something isn't available.  I will do my best to respond promptly and keep the list updated.

So here's what I have for sale! All are PSA graded.  I can send you scans upon request, please provide your e-mail address and allow up to 48 hours for me to respond (I travel for business and have family responsibilities which limit my ability to respond immediately).
